olls of toilet paper sitting on the back of the toilet....GROSS!!   I probably won't go out of my way to make it back to The Grind, there are just too many other burger places out there right now and they don't have nearly enough variety to eat there on a regular basis. I know that In-N-Out gets away with the concept, but at $1.50 per burger that is acceptable, not at the $10 a la carte price tag at The Grind.

